3
00:00:45,583 --> 00:00:47,416
Hi there! Would you...

4
00:00:50,083 --> 00:00:51,541
[ROKA groans]

5
00:01:02,208 --> 00:01:04,833
[KAZAMA] Hey, you all right?
Think you dropped this.

6
00:01:13,541 --> 00:01:15,083
Best watch yourself, huh?

7
00:01:16,833 --> 00:01:17,750
[ROKA] Thank y--

8
00:01:17,833 --> 00:01:19,625
