9
00:01:19,708 --> 00:01:20,916
Hey, how's it goin'?

10
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,166
[KAZAMA] Meh. Y'know.

11
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:23,166
[YOKOSHIMA] Whaddya say
