00:01:52,583 --> 00:01:54,041
with a gut like that.

23
00:01:54,125 --> 00:01:56,375
[GUY 1A] Long Mountain Nagayama.

24
00:01:56,458 --> 00:01:57,916
[GUY 1B] What does
that even mean?

25
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,833
[GUY 1A] And their
ringleader, uh, um...

26
00:02:00,916 --> 00:02:03,541
Hang on, it'll come
to me... Damn it.

27
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,916
It's part of the gang's name!

28
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,291
If you're givin' us
a runnin' commentary,

29
00:02:08,375 --> 00:02:09,500
have your ducks in a row!

30
00:02:09,583 --> 00:02:11,958
[GUY 1B] Run for your life!

31
00:02:12,041 --> 00:02:13,750
Sorry, man. Our bad.

32
00:02:13,833 --> 00:02:16,083
We just kinda
naturally stand out.

33
00:02:16,166 --> 00:02:17,875
[KAZAMA]
Oh, yeah? Ya think?

34
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:22,708
Way to be here two minutes and
already get slapped with a rep.

35
00:02:22,791 --> 00:02:25,875
Why people gotta go stereotypin'
juvenile delinquents like that?

36
00:02:25,958 --> 00:02:27,458
[KAZAMA sighs]

37
00:02:27,541 --> 00:02:29,708
