for the straight
and narrow now, boys...

41
00:02:36,375 --> 00:02:39,875
'cause I plan on using these
fists to conquer the school!

42
00:02:39,958 --> 00:02:42,166
[GIRL 1A] I think I finally
learned how to play a "fa."

43
00:02:42,250 --> 00:02:43,708
[GIRL 1C] Remi!

44
00:02:53,458 --> 00:02:55,750
[CHITOSE] Still no new
candidates for membership.

45
00:02:57,625 --> 00:03:00,083
If things keep going like this,
we're destined to lose the club.

46
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:01,916
Why does the school care
if we stay like we are?

47
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,500
We're big enough!

48
00:03:03,583 --> 00:03:06,291
They care simply because we
call ourselves a culture club

49
00:03:06,375 --> 00:03:08,708
without having produced
a shred of culture.

50
00:03:08,791 --> 00:03:11,166
Ugh. What do they want
from us? We play games!

51
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:12,916
Apparently that's not enough.

52
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,750
