with the Game Creation handle,

53
00:03:15,833 --> 00:03:18,125
we'll actually have
to create games.

54
00:03:18,208 --> 00:03:19,416
Oh, yeah.

55
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:21,208
That really just
dawned on you?

56
00:03:21,291 --> 00:03:23,083
Until today, I've been
able to navigate us

57
00:03:23,166 --> 00:03:25,708
around that little
technicality, but...

58
00:03:25,791 --> 00:03:26,833
The fact is we're short

59
00:03:26,916 --> 00:03:28,958
the minimum number
of members required.

60
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:32,250
