around doing jack squat.

61
00:03:32,333 --> 00:03:33,625
So when's the
recruitment deadline?

62
00:03:33,708 --> 00:03:35,375
--[CHITOSE] Today.
--[SAKURA groans]

63
00:03:39,041 --> 00:03:40,750
[YOKOSHIMA] Hahaha!
Here's the deal, fellas.

64
00:03:40,833 --> 00:03:43,083
If the Kazama Gang's gonna let
the li'l sheeple around here

65
00:03:43,166 --> 00:03:45,458
know who's boss,
we gots to strut our stuff!

66
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:48,375
Couple a' hostile takeovers,
maybe a turf war.

67
00:03:48,458 --> 00:03:49,750
I suppose we could
always make a play

68
00:03:49,833 --> 00:03:51,416
for the Golf Bag
Gang's territory.

69
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:54,291
The Golf Bag Gang?
That can't be their real name.

70
00:03:54,375 --> 00:03:56,583
[YOKOSHIMA] Or... We could
run a protection racket

71
00:03:56,666 --> 00:03:59,250
on the culture clubs! Dude!
Think of the graft!

72
00:03:59,333 --> 00:04:00,250
It'd be awesome!

73
00:04:00,333 --> 00:04:01,625
Nice.

74
00:04:01,708 --> 00:04:03,750
I mean, c'mon, what
self-respecting evil overlords

75
00:04:03,833 --> 00:04:06,166
buy their own manga,
am I right?

76
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:09,166
Weren't you guys bitchin' about
stereotypes two minutes ago?

77
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:10,250
[YOKOSHIMA]
You said it yourself--

78
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:12,250
we've gotta conquer the school!

79
00:04:13,458 --> 00:04:14,541
