84
00:04:24,375 --> 00:04:27,583
Uh... This fire is nothing
but an illusion, good sir.

85
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:29,916
Yeah, well, your "illusion's"
gonna burn this place down!

86
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,083
[NAGAYAMA] Kenji!
Fire Extinguisher!

87
00:04:32,166 --> 00:04:33,458
Right, yes!

88
00:04:33,541 --> 00:04:35,500
Ladies, please step aside!

89
00:04:38,166 --> 00:04:41,041
Yeah! 'Cause that's
what's up, fire!

90
00:04:46,458 --> 00:04:49,916
[ALL] Hooray!
The day is saved!

91
00:04:51,083 --> 00:04:53,083
[KAZAMA] Whoa.
What am I doing?

92
00:04:53,166 --> 00:04:55,666
