one way or the other?

93
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,625
You handled that
illusion admirably.

94
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:00,333
[KAZAMA] Were you
trying to kill us all?

95
00:05:02,291 --> 00:05:05,375
How'd you manage to get the
damn thing started anyway?

96
00:05:07,958 --> 00:05:09,166
[KAZAMA] Fireworks?

97
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:10,500
[YOKOSHIMA trembles]

98
00:05:10,583 --> 00:05:12,708
You'll never know how much
we appreciate the help.

99
00:05:12,791 --> 00:05:16,375
Yokoshima! What did you
do to him? Nagaya--!

100
00:05:17,833 --> 00:05:19,958
