leak to the outside world.

106
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:32,541
So we're erasing your memories
of what just happened.

107
00:05:32,625 --> 00:05:33,750
You girls are nuts!

108
00:05:33,833 --> 00:05:35,291
[ROKA]
I'm sorry.

109
00:05:36,333 --> 00:05:39,208
You've stolen a forbidden
glance into my fire magic.

110
00:05:39,291 --> 00:05:41,041
I'm compelled to
make you forget.

111
00:05:41,125 --> 00:05:42,291
I've done what now?

112
00:05:42,375 --> 00:05:44,041
Are you tryin' to
say you're magical?

113
00:05:44,125 --> 00:05:46,708
[ROKA] Each of us here is an
elemental magic wielder, yes.

114
00:05:46,791 --> 00:05:49,500
[KAZAMA] You're all out
of your freakin' minds!

115
00:05:49,583 --> 00:05:51,083
Let go of me, I'm serious!

116
00:05:51,166 --> 00:05:52,208
Invoke Water Lock!

117
00:05:52,291 --> 00:05:53,458
Invoke Lightning Lock!

118
00:05:53,541 --> 00:05:55,583
Ugh! That's not
even a real thing!

119
