trembling to its knees!

127
00:06:21,791 --> 00:06:22,958
[MINAMI] It's okay,
I don't think her wounds

128
00:06:23,041 --> 00:06:24,541
are beyond healing!

129
00:06:24,625 --> 00:06:28,291
[KAZAMA] Alrighty, then. Maybe
her and fire really are a thing.

130
00:06:30,166 --> 00:06:31,916
[KAZAMA]
Hm? Uh--?

131
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:34,166
