156
00:07:31,583 --> 00:07:34,541
[CHITOSE] What kind of man
leaves his friends to die?

157
00:07:34,625 --> 00:07:36,791
[KAZAMA] Least in this scenario
one of us survives!

158
00:07:36,875 --> 00:07:39,375
Why do I feel the need to
plead my case with the enemy?

159
00:07:39,458 --> 00:07:41,041
Turn around and
face your fate!

160
00:07:41,125 --> 00:07:43,791
Uh, that might've
been a little harsh.

161
00:07:43,875 --> 00:07:46,916
[KAZAMA] Aahhh!
They're gonna kill me!

162
00:07:49,541 --> 00:07:50,916
[CHITOSE] It was
a figure of speech!

163
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,625
Figure of speech, my butt!
You're homicidal!

164
00:07:53,708 --> 00:07:59,291
[KAZAMA yells, pants]

165
00:07:59,375 --> 00:08:03,041
Nooo!

166
00:08:05,625 --> 00:08:07,708
[KAZAMA pants]

167
00:08:07,791 --> 00:08:10,375
You're good. Calm down,
you managed to shake 'em.

168
00:08:10,458 --> 00:08:14,041
What kinda club're they runnin',
anyway? They're all insane.

169
00:08:15,583 --> 00:08:17,500
Excuse me.

170
00:08:17,583 --> 00:08:19,791
Fire magic girl!

171
00:08:19,875 --> 00:08:21,833
I never said thank you.

172
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:23,291
Thank you?

173
00:08:23,375 --> 00:08:24,666
For coming to our rescue.

174
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,625
Uh... What now?

175
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:27,875
We've learned our lesson.

176
00:08:27,958 --> 00:08:29,916
No more fireworks
in the clubroom.

177
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,208
Well, good for you!

178
00:08:31,291 --> 00:08:32,625
What were they doing there
in the first place?

179
00:08:32,708 --> 00:08:34,083
We need new members
and I thought

180
00:08:34,166 --> 00:08:36,458
a pyrotechnic display
would be good marketing.

181
00:08:36,541 --> 00:08:39,041
You could've burned the
whole school to the ground!

182
00:08:39,125 --> 00:08:40,916
That's true. Why didn't
I think of that?

183
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,875
[KAZAMA]
That's not what I meant!

184
00:08:42,958 --> 00:08:44,875
Oh, and thanks
for this morning.

185
00:08:44,958 --> 00:08:47,000
You picked up those
flyers for me.

186
00:08:47,083 --> 00:08:48,666
It was a nice thing to do.

187
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:52,166
Uh... Wait.

188
00:08:52,250 --> 00:08:54,708
So... You're the girl I saw
at the gate this morning?

189
00:08:54,791 --> 00:08:56,208
