for that schizophrenic club?

191
00:08:59,166 --> 00:09:00,458
Schizophrenic?

192
00:09:00,541 --> 00:09:02,083
Look, just...
Just leave me alone

193
00:09:02,166 --> 00:09:03,500
and we'll call it even, alright?

194
00:09:03,583 --> 00:09:07,041
I'm glad I could give you
a hand. Have a nice life.

195
00:09:07,125 --> 00:09:08,791
[ROKA] For the record,
my club could really use

196
00:09:08,875 --> 00:09:10,250
somebody like you.

197
00:09:10,333 --> 00:09:11,750
The club's yours?

198
00:09:11,833 --> 00:09:15,458
Roka Shibasaki, at your service.
Game Club President.

199
00:09:15,541 --> 00:09:17,916
I thought it was called
the Game Creation Club.

200
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,125
[ROKA] Whatever.
I'm recruiting you.

201
00:09:20,208 --> 00:09:22,041
Thanks, but that's
not my scene.

202
00:09:22,125 --> 00:09:25,875
[ROKA] It's not just about
gaming. It's about making games.

203
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,541
What're you doing?
You know your ultimate

204
00:09:31,625 --> 00:09:34,416
fire-based whatever attack
isn't gonna work on me.

205
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,000
[ROKA] My fire magic
is mere camouflage.

206
00:09:37,083 --> 00:09:38,333
[KAZAMA]
Huh?

207
00:09:38,416 --> 00:09:43,708
Beneath this veneer.
I am a wielder of darkness.

208
00:09:43,791 --> 00:09:46,416
Uh, okay.

209
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:49,208
[KAZAMA screams]

210
00:09:52,958 --> 00:09:54,000
[YOKOSHIMA] What the...?

211
00:09:54,083 --> 00:09:55,541
[NAGAYAMA]
Did I miss somethin'?

212
00:09:55,625 --> 00:09:57,583
[YOKOSHIMA]
Where did Kenji go?

213
00:09:57,666 --> 00:09:59,041
[KAZAMA]
I'm in the dark!

214
00:09:59,125 --> 00:10:00,208
[KAZAMA screams]

215
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:03,250
Help me! I can't see!
Where am I?

216
00:10:03,333 --> 00:10:06,208
As of this moment, two paths
are open before you.

217
00:10:06,291 --> 00:10:07,958
On the one hand, you do
the respectable thing

218
00:10:08,041 --> 00:10:11,500
and join the Game Creation Club.
And on the other...

219
00:10:15,833 --> 00:10:18,375
[ROKA] Choose wisely,
hapless traveler.

220
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:20,416
[KAZAMA]
Okay! Fine, I'll join!

221
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,416
Just take this thing
off a' me! Please!

222
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:24,458
Now that's what
I like to hear.

223
00:10:34,375 --> 00:10:37,333
Starting over. My name
is Roka Shibasaki.

224
00:10:37,416 --> 00:10:39,541
Game Creation Club President.

225
00:10:39,625 --> 00:10:43,041
Second-year Chitose
Karasuyama. What's up?

226
00:10:43,125 --> 00:10:45,166
First-year Sakura Mizukami.

227
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,750
[KAZAMA] I don't care what your
names are, take this thing off!!

228
00:10:47,833 --> 00:10:50,083
[CHITOSE] I'm gonna need
you to pay attention, noob.

229
00:10:50,166 --> 00:10:51,166
[KAZAMA]
What're you doing?

230
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,291
[CHITOSE] Huh.
He seems to be caressing

231
00:10:52,375 --> 00:10:54,250
the sole of my shoe
with his face.

232
00:10:54,333 --> 00:10:55,583
Do you have a foot fetish?

233
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:59,458
[KAZAMA] No, I don't!
That's gross. Cut it out!

234
00:10:59,541 --> 00:11:00,583
What's wrong with you?

235
00:11:00,666 --> 00:11:01,833
Sorry about the ropes.

236
00:11:01,916 --> 00:11:03,250
We didn't think you'd
hear us out otherwise.

237
00:11:03,333 --> 00:11:04,500
You ever stop and
think maybe you're

238
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:06,041
takin' things a little too far?

239
00:11:06,125 --> 00:11:08,583
All right then, Mr. Foot Fetish,
you've heard our names.

240
00:11:08,666 --> 00:11:10,208
No! Knock it off!
You're tryin' to make me out

