373
00:17:00,541 --> 00:17:02,375
We were inseparable;
but for some reason

374
00:17:02,458 --> 00:17:04,166
best known to yourselves
you fell into a life

375
00:17:04,250 --> 00:17:05,958
of thuggishness
and petty crime.

376
00:17:06,041 --> 00:17:07,916
Why did you turn
your backs on me?

377
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,916
[KAZAMA] Will you just tell
us what you're doing here?

378
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,916
Ah. Yes, of course.

379
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,708
Kenji. Word through the
grapevine is... is, well,

380
00:17:16,791 --> 00:17:19,000
