the Two Brothers,

396
00:17:55,041 --> 00:17:58,166
and the Band of Fourteen
Devils all went into hiding!

397
00:17:58,250 --> 00:17:59,708
Wait, you're tellin' me
this place already had

398
00:17:59,791 --> 00:18:01,333
