Oh, please! As far as everyone
else in school is concerned,

400
00:18:03,583 --> 00:18:04,625
you lot might as well
have just fallen

401
00:18:04,708 --> 00:18:06,333
off the back of a turnip truck!

402
00:18:06,416 --> 00:18:08,791
