Ouch.

403
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,375
Back to Miss Karasuyama.

404
00:18:10,458 --> 00:18:14,041
My being Vice President makes
she and I eternal arch nemeses.

405
00:18:14,125 --> 00:18:15,750
Condemned to fight
to the bitter end!

406
00:18:15,833 --> 00:18:17,458
Hey, I want in on
some of that action!

407
00:18:17,541 --> 00:18:18,458
Hell, yeah!

408
00:18:18,541 --> 00:18:20,750
Don't forget
to include me!

409
00:18:21,791 --> 00:18:23,958
