00:20:55,208 --> 00:20:57,750
I will surpass
your earth magic!

475
00:20:57,833 --> 00:21:01,041
Never let it be said I don't
admire your moxy, VP, now die!

476
00:21:01,125 --> 00:21:05,875
[ATARU and CHITOSE struggle]

477
00:21:05,958 --> 00:21:08,250
[ATARU] Kenji!
A little help, please?

478
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:10,208
[KAZAMA] I'm sorry,
you need me for something?

479
00:21:10,291 --> 00:21:12,416
Damn it, man! We can't
do this without you!

480
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,166
How am I supposed
to turn my life around

481
00:21:14,250 --> 00:21:16,208
with you playing
tic-tac-toe?

482
00:21:16,291 --> 00:21:18,250
[KAZAMA] Well you sure didn't
need me to get this far.

483
00:21:18,333 --> 00:21:19,916
You, uh... you
got two minutes.

484
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,458
That's as long as
I can keep this up.

485
00:21:21,541 --> 00:21:22,250
[KAZAMA]
Nagayama!

486
00:21:22,333 --> 00:21:23,416
Yeah, better make it one.

487
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:24,500
[KAZAMA]
Seriously?

488
00:21:24,583 --> 00:21:26,500
Huh. That's not a
whole lot of time.

489
00:21:26,583 --> 00:21:28,791
But if I start now,
that one minute...

490
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:32,458
[KAZAMA growls]

491
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:33,666
[KAZAMA]
Hyah!

492
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:34,833
[ATARU]
Go!

493
00:21:34,916 --> 00:21:35,500
[KAZAMA]
Hyah!

494
00:21:35,583 --> 00:21:36,625
[CHITOSE gasps]

495
00:21:36,708 --> 00:21:37,791
[KAZAMA]
...should be enough!

496
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:40,500
[ATARU &amp; KAZAMA grunt]

497
00:21:46,833 --> 00:21:48,833
I set out to try
and save my friends.

498
00:21:48,916 --> 00:21:51,250
But when it was all said
and done, you saved me.

499
00:21:51,333 --> 00:21:52,833
Forget about it.

500
00:21:52,916 --> 00:21:55,458
I was itchin' for some payback
anyway, so it all worked out.

501
00:21:55,541 --> 00:21:57,333
[CHITOSE]
Bravo.

502
00:21:57,416 --> 00:22:01,333
I didn't approve of Roka
enlisting you at first.

503
00:22:01,416 --> 00:22:05,791
But I suppose...
opinions can change.

504
00:22:05,875 --> 00:22:08,375
Even if I have
won this round.

505
00:22:08,458 --> 00:22:10,333
[KAZAMA &amp; ATARU]
Uh... Uhhh...

506
00:22:10,416 --> 00:22:13,041
[YOKOSHIMA]
Run away!

507
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:20,541
[KAZAMA]
Ehhh...

508
00:22:20,625 --> 00:22:22,500
[ROKA]
Hey, Kenji!

509
00:22:22,583 --> 00:22:23,958
Oh, it's you.

510
00:22:24,041 --> 00:22:26,333
FYI, we meet up
four times a week.

511
00:22:26,416 --> 00:22:29,166
Tuesday, Wednesday,
Thursday and Friday.

512
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:33,166
Whatever. Look... How come
you wanted me to join?

513
00:22:33,250 --> 00:22:35,000
Why, do you think
the club is dumb?

514
00:22:35,083 --> 00:22:36,875
Are you backing out?

515
00:22:49,625 --> 00:22:52,291
I already submitted the
enrollment form, so...

516
00:22:52,375 --> 00:22:55,041
Guess I'm here to stay.

517
00:22:55,125 --> 00:22:56,750
[ROKA] Awesome!

